{
  "_comment": [
    "Span nodes exactly as Phoenix GraphQL returns them to navigator.js",
    "(`attributes` is the JSON string Phoenix serializes, nested/unflattened;",
    "`parentId` is the parent's OTel span id, null on roots).",
    "",
    "talon_trace models a real Talon run (producer: kestrel-talon via",
    "tracing.py KestrelTracer): the run ROOT carries kestrel.agent_name=='talon'",
    "and kestrel.run_id; the worker split lives ONLY on child stage spans —",
    "as kestrel.stage (gate), a prefixed agent-name variant (talon/review), or",
    "both (talon/implement) — and NO talon span stamps kestrel.session_id or",
    "session.id. The run id is the only session identity available.",
    "",
    "emitter_session models a hook.py session: root marker + summary carry",
    "kestrel.session_id; the tool child carries the agent name only."
  ],
